curam.util.resources

Interface EnvironmentConstants.BatchLauncher

  • Enclosing interface:
    EnvironmentConstants

    public static interface EnvironmentConstants.BatchLauncher
    These settings configure the behavior of Curam when problems occur invoking batch programs.
